{"tid":1462600,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［檢討］尋找和你飛行動的共識","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:55.000Z","uid":387,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"65e3b0f4dc9011df830a6b8b4fbbff21faaddc89","tid":1462600,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:56:29.000Z","msg":"見到大家分岐好大<br />\n想俾啲睇法 唔認同請直接屌<br />\n<br />\n首先 <br />\n和你飛係終極和理非行動<br />\n全世界都睇住你地<br />\n唔會 都唔應該有任何肢體衝突<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n和你飛的主要目的係做文宣<br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n尋日取消只係side effect<br />\n係當人多既時候先會做到<br />\n<br />\n結論<br />\n唔好心急<br />\n唔好俾尋日一時既勝利沖昏頭腦<br />\n群眾運動最重要就係人數<br />\n人數唔夠唔好夾硬黎<br />\n係和理非場合記住一樣野<br />\n凡事留一事 唔好做盡<br />\n個觀感會好好多<br />\n當然 個成效會唔會比你直接塞<br />\n更加快更加好<br />\n老實講 唔會<br />\n但係長期黎講一定要留返機場依個地方俾和理非<br />\n因為基本上全港黎計 果度係最安全既地方"},{"pid":"f6636b4e2430736f466c4e1c254de09db544b923","tid":1462600,"uid":294974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:57:18.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"8ed692adabdaa1631151f062904a6aaa73955d6d","tid":1462600,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:59:45.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"08266011877c7c6d68cd098913fd301448971708","tid":1462600,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:59:59.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"30c67d0e51766e85a39a1d19a60503d682e2740e","tid":1462600,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:00:28.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"bbc44da9a3b731fdf9bd869d0e4babff847080dd","tid":14